            "<li>Langmead B, Trapnell C, Pop M, Salzberg SL. (2009) Ultrafast and memory-efficient alignment of short DNA sequences to the human genome. Genome Biology, 10(3), R25. doi: 10.1186/gb-2009-10-3-r25</li>",
